# Website Analysis Checklist: https://airecomed-web-b4521.web.app/

- [ ] Visit the homepage and take a screenshot
- [ ] Read all text content on the homepage
- [ ] Identify and navigate to all sections/pages (About, Services, Products, etc.)
- [ ] Take screenshots of each important section/page
- [ ] Identify brand name and tagline
- [ ] Identify products/services
- [ ] Identify target audience
- [ ] Identify value proposition
- [ ] Collect contact information (phone, email, address, city/country)
- [ ] Collect social media links
- [ ] List navigation menu items
- [ ] Identify CTAs
- [ ] Note color scheme and visual style
- [ ] Collect pricing information (if any)
- [ ] Collect testimonials/reviews (if any)
- [ ] List any blog posts/articles
- [ ] List footer content
- [ ] Compile a final report
